# Run Together Core

- Treat run creation, join flow, participants, geo/maps, auth, and notifications as sensitive MVP systems.
- Keep the product lightweight.
- Avoid adding complex social features unless explicitly requested.
- Preserve the simple create -> list -> join flow.
- Keep future native mobile migration low-pain.
- Keep business logic separate from UI where practical.
- For geo/map or notification bugs, start with audit-only before implementation.
